Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.39,0:04:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:263393,265929}No matter what happens,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.92,0:04:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:265929,270500}it is unthinkable for a lady from my family\Nto marry some piano teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.50,0:04:32.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:270500,272669}I will never allow it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.06,0:04:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:273069,276840}Geneviève. You have\Nto remember about your pedigree.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.84,0:04:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:276840,278508}You know what I mean, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.14,0:04:44.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:282145,284147}Father. Mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.34,0:04:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:284347,286916}It is two people fighting for their lives\Nwe're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.91,0:04:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:286916,288918}Now is not the time to lecture her\Nabout pedigree and whatnot.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.91,0:04:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:288918,292355}We shall focus\Non stopping these two.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.28,0:04:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:293289,296159}Geneviève, I believe\Nyou do realize what you ought to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.89,0:04:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:296893,298194}Andréa…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.19,0:05:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:298194,301464}An excellent army officer\Nagainst a pianist.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.46,0:05:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:301464,303500}You want neither\Nto lose their life.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.60,0:05:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:304601,306469}Am I right, Geneviève?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.67,0:05:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:312675,316045}Ms. Isabelle, you have a guest.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.04,0:05:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:316045,318181}I'll be right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.82,0:05:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:324821,327457}Hey, Isabelle.\NHow have you been?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.69,0:05:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:327690,329192}It's you again?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.19,0:05:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:329192,332295}Yup. It's me, Jean Clément\Nwith my daily marriage proposal.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.02,0:05:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:333029,335465}I'm not in the mood\Nfor your jokes today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.46,0:05:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:335465,338968}Jean, do you even know\Nwhat's going on tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.96,0:05:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:338968,341971}Mr. Victor and Mr. Jules\Nwill fight in a duel, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.97,0:05:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:341971,344908}And three days from today,\Nyou're moving to Versailles.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.90,0:05:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:344908,347310}I know your schedule\Nlike the back of my hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.31,0:05:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:347310,350146}You know all of this\Nand you still come here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.14,0:05:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:350146,352582}What is wrong with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.58,0:05:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:352582,357754}Especially in such a serious situation,\Nyou should be like me and try to have fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.42,0:06:01.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:359422,361891}I see. Try to have fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.09,0:06:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:362091,363927}Here. Such fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.12,0:06:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:366129,368698}I'm sick of you! Get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.46,0:06:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:370466,372068}Isabelle, I can't leave you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.00,0:06:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:373002,375839}It's true that I was weak\Nand a crybaby when we were kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.83,0:06:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:375839,377774}But I'm different now, Isabelle!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.77,0:06:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:377774,378842}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.84,0:06:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:378842,383847}Now I have the courage to pick up a rose\Nyou rejected and attach it to your chest!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.01,0:06:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:385014,386683}See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.95,0:06:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:389953,393089}"I have the courage to pick up a rose\Nyou rejected". She'll be head over heels!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.02,0:06:39.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:397026,399095}Stop strutting\Nlike the king of the roost.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.09,0:06:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:399095,401464}You're ten years too young\Nto hit on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.00,0:06:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:411007,412742}Nobody said it'd be easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.26,0:07:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:433263,434330}Victor.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.93,0:07:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:434931,435732}Victor.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.86,0:07:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:436866,439002}I see you're as good as ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.00,0:07:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:439002,442605}But you never know\Nwhat can happen in a duel.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.07,0:07:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:443072,444407}I know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.40,0:07:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:444407,447610}I'm sorry on behalf of my sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.61,0:07:29.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:447610,449879}But in the end,\Nit's only about some woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.87,0:07:32.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:449879,452015}It's not a matter\Nworth of a soldier's life.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.28,0:07:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:455285,458187}Soon this place will be swarming\Nwith the Prussian army.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.18,0:07:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:458187,460590}You're too important\Nfor the defense of Paris.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.35,0:07:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:463359,465461}I don't want you to risk your life\Nover a mere woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.46,0:07:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:465461,467063}Andréa.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.06,0:07:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:467063,469332}I'm not taking part in this duel\Nfor a woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.10,0:07:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:474103,475538}It's about pride.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.58,0:08:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:486582,488551}Your pride as a soldier?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.55,0:08:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:488551,492221}A high-ranking army officer, whose bride\Nwas stolen by an impoverished pianist.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.58,0:08:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:492588,494123}This is who I am now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.12,0:08:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:494123,497226}Love is fickle.\NI'm fine with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.22,0:08:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:497226,500363}But how can I live as a soldier\Nwith a stain on his pride?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.26,0:08:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:501264,503633}If I can't protect\Neven my own pride,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.63,0:08:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:503633,506903}how can I protect the pride of France?\NHow can I defend Paris?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.40,0:08:32.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:510406,512275}I might be old-fashioned.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.27,0:08:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:512275,514377}But that's just who I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.58,0:08:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:524587,528558}{\i1}Soon after a storm broke out,\Nunusual for this time of year.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.55,0:08:51.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:528558,531494}{\i1}The city was bathed in a downpour,\Nthough it was only afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.49,0:08:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:531494,533863}{\i1}There was no one on the streets.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.86,0:08:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:533863,537367}{\i1}The only sound in Paris\Nwas heavy rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.36,0:09:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:537367,542205}{\i1}However, the Prussian army\Ndid not rest
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.20,0:09:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:542205,545208}{\i1}and mercilessly continued\Ntheir advance on Paris.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.65,0:09:25.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:563659,565495}Jules, I heard everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.49,0:09:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:565495,566996}Stop this foolishness.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.99,0:09:28.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:566996,568197}Foolishness?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.19,0:09:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:568197,569866}You called it foolishness?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.86,0:09:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:569866,572502}I did. Your opponent\Nis a trained soldier.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.50,0:09:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:572502,575738}You never drew a gun before.\NYou're no match for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.73,0:09:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:575738,578474}You're telling me to forfeit\Nand swallow the shame of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.47,0:09:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:578474,580009}Where's the shame in it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.00,0:09:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:580009,581978}You have important\Nthings to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.97,0:09:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:581978,587450}Have you forgotten the words of the oath\Nwe made with the people in this cafe?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.75,0:09:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:587750,589752}Paris is our city!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.35,0:09:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:590353,591320}Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.32,0:09:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:591320,593723}Who is going to\Ndefend our city? Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.72,0:09:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:593723,596426}The army? The politicians?\NThe aristocrats?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.42,0:09:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:596426,598428}No. It'll be us!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.42,0:09:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:598428,599662}It'll be us!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.66,0:10:00.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:599662,600997}We'll defend Paris!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.99,0:10:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:600997,602632}We'll defend Paris!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.63,0:10:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:602632,604000}Defend Paris!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.00,0:10:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:604000,605301}Defend Paris!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.00,0:10:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:611007,613409}You are one of those leaders.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.40,0:10:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:613409,618081}Don't give up your life\Nfor some rich chick you cannot have!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.61,0:10:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:620616,624454}Do you… Have you ever been\Nin love with someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.42,0:10:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:630426,635531}A man is willing to risk his life for a woman.\NI happen to love that woman as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.53,0:10:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:635531,638301}But I am going to love her\Nmore than anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.10,0:10:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:643106,647043}I love Geneviève more than\NI value the life of that man.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.31,0:10:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:649312,652148}Let it go.\NTime heals wounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.11,0:10:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:655118,656586}Don't die in vain!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.98,0:10:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:656986,658955}Die in vain?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.95,0:11:01.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:658955,661390}I love the city of Paris.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.39,0:11:02.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:661390,662992}That is why\NI will fight to defend it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.86,0:11:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:664861,667063}The same goes\Nfor the people I love.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.29,0:11:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:668297,669899}It is not in vain.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.54,0:11:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:686549,688050}Victor is serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.05,0:11:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:688050,692288}The only chance to stop the duel\Nis to make Jules apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.78,0:11:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:692788,695458}If we don't stop them,\NJules is going to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.45,0:11:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:695458,698327}Sister. Can't we do something?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.69,0:11:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:699695,701264}There is nothing I can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.26,0:11:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:701264,703466}If the worst happens,\NI don't want to live anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.46,0:11:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:703466,705001}What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.53,0:11:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:706536,708738}Are you telling me…\Nto break up with Jules?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.14,0:11:54.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:711140,714110}Do you have any better idea\Nhow to save them?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.37,0:11:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:716379,717346}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.34,0:11:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:717346,718347}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.34,0:11:59.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:718347,719916}Anything but that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.39,0:12:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:734397,739502}{\i1}Geneviève went\Nto Jules' apartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.50,0:12:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:739502,742138}{\i1}She was about to say goodbye\Nfor the last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.77,0:12:28.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:745775,748744}{\i1}In order to stop the duel and\Nmake sure nobody dies,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.74,0:12:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:748744,753482}{\i1}Geneviève had no choice\Nbut to break up with Jules.
Comment: 0,0:12:41.89,0:12:41.89,Default,[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:761891,761891}Part B
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.30,0:12:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:777306,779008}Ms. Geneviève.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.00,0:13:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:779008,780676}Thank you, Gaston.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.27,0:13:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:781277,784046}I can go back by myself.\NYou can go back now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.04,0:13:07.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:784046,787416}All right.\NPlease be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.56,0:13:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:801564,802898}Geneviève!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.93,0:13:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:803933,805301}I came to say goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.87,0:13:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:807870,809572}Don't go to the duel.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.13,0:13:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:810139,812441}Just let it go.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.14,0:13:35.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:813142,815878}I am going to marry Victor.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.41,0:13:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:816412,817747}Geneviève!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.81,0:13:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:818814,819882}Geneviève, don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.91,0:13:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:821917,826489}Until now, I've been running away from you,\Nusing your happiness as my excuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.48,0:13:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:826489,829458}But that duel\Nactually opened my eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.45,0:13:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:829458,831327}You shouldn't run away\Nfrom the ones you love.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.32,0:13:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:831327,833329}You shouldn't let go of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.32,0:13:55.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:833329,835665}You should stand up\Nand fight for them!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.50,0:13:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:837500,838668}Jules…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.24,0:14:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:845241,846909}Look around.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.48,0:14:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:854483,856485}That is our city.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.48,0:14:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:856485,859989}Filthy and cramped,\Nthis is our Paris.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.98,0:14:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:859989,864327}This is where we grew up.\NThis is where we live.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.32,0:14:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:864327,866896}It is a completely different\Nworld to what you're used to.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.89,0:14:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:866896,869365}It's full of poverty and suffering.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.56,0:14:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:869565,872335}Still, we're trying\Nour best to survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.33,0:14:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:872335,873269}I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.50,0:14:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:873502,876138}But I'm begging you,\Ndon't go to that duel.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.43,0:14:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:876439,879475}That means to let you go.\NThis is something I cannot do.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.47,0:14:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:879475,881177}I want you to live!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.54,0:14:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:882545,883512}I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.51,0:14:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:883512,885381}I don't want to die, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.74,0:14:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:885748,888217}But if it's for the things I love,\NI'm not afraid of dying.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.62,0:14:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:893622,895791}Jules…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.12,0:14:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:896125,898160}I don't want to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.03,0:15:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:902031,904033}It is time for you\Nto leave, Geneviève.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.30,0:15:09.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:905301,909972}As long as the duel is not settled,\Nyou are not my woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.81,0:15:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:919815,920383}Ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.78,0:15:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:921784,924253}Ms. Geneviève,\NI came to pick you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.78,0:15:26.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:924787,926055}Gaston…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.42,0:15:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:926422,929925}I am your loyal servant.\NI will always stand beside you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.33,0:15:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:935331,938401}{\i1}The duel that was about to take place\Ncould have only one outcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.40,0:15:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:938401,943472}{\i1}Both Jules and Geneviève\Nknew that all too well.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.47,0:15:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:943472,948177}{\i1}Neither Jules or Geneviève\Nhad any hope for the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.48,0:15:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:952481,954784}{\i1}An old, worn out piano.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.78,0:15:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:954784,957119}{\i1}We've been through\Na lot together.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.11,0:15:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:957119,959021}{\i1}Today might be our last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.30,0:16:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:975304,979608}{\i1}Jules' piano continued\Nto ring until dawn.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.17,0:16:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:980176,985448}{\i1}That night, nobody could sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.84,0:17:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1047843,1051380}Hey, Jules!\NAre you going, after all?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.02,0:17:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1064026,1065294}Hyah!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.86,0:17:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1068864,1071267}Why can't I go with them?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.26,0:17:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1071267,1074637}Duels between men are not something\Na young lady should watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.88,0:18:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1090886,1094056}{\i1}Isabelle felt uneasy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.76,0:18:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1097760,1103365}{\i1}Isabelle had a longing for Victor\Nthat could only be described as being in love.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.54,0:18:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1114543,1116211}{\i1}Victor…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.21,0:18:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1116211,1120549}{\i1}Dear God, please protect Victor.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.18,0:18:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1125187,1127856}Jean? What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.85,0:18:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1127856,1130125}I arranged a horse\Nfor us in secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.12,0:18:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1130125,1133095}Isabelle, you're in love\Nwith Captain Langlois, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.83,0:18:56.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1134830,1136899}You can't go to see your crush,{NOTE:xxx}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.89,0:18:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1136899,1139401}but you have me,\Nyour childhood friend!{NOTE:xxx}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.40,0:19:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1139401,1143606}Let's go.\NI'll show you my rival's duel.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.60,0:19:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1143606,1144940}Jean?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.00,0:19:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1146008,1147810}Come on, hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.20,0:19:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1175204,1177906}Nobody will see us from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.64,0:19:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1181644,1184279}I'll ask you this one last time.\NIs either of you willing to step down?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.41,0:19:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1185414,1188417}Captain Langlois, know that\NI have no grudge against you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.41,0:19:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1188417,1192087}But for Geneviève,\NI will fight you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.08,0:19:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1192087,1194423}A duel does not need words.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.62,0:20:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1199628,1202665}Both pistols have one bullet.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.66,0:20:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1202665,1206335}I hope that no matter how this ends up,\Nthere will be no grudge.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.33,0:20:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1206335,1209038}Jules, you pick the pistol.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.37,0:20:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1210372,1211874}Whichever you like best.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.21,0:20:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1217212,1219248}Do you know how to shoot it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.24,0:20:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1219248,1220382}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.52,0:20:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1231527,1235731}Let the duel between Victor Langlois\Nand Jules Francoeur begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.70,0:20:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1239702,1242504}Walk forward 10 steps,\Nturn around and shoot.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.40,0:20:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1243405,1244707}One.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.70,0:20:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1244707,1245708}Two.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.70,0:20:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1245708,1246809}Three.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.80,0:20:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1246809,1247910}Four.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.91,0:20:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1247910,1249078}Five.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.07,0:20:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1249078,1250245}Six.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.24,0:20:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1250245,1251380}Seven.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.38,0:20:52.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1251380,1252414}Eight.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.41,0:20:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1252414,1253515}Nine.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.51,0:20:54.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1253515,1254817}Ten!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.76,0:21:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1300763,1302097}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.09,0:21:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1302097,1303599}Don't do it, I'm begging you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.59,0:21:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1303599,1306135}Victor, if you must shoot,\Nshoot at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.60,0:21:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1308604,1309772}Stay out of this, Geneviève!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.77,0:21:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1309772,1310906}Move out of the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.90,0:21:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1310906,1311640}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.64,0:21:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1311640,1312808}Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.80,0:21:56.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1312808,1316311}Geneviève, do you want me\Nto look like a coward?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.31,0:21:56.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1316311,1316879}Jules!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.87,0:22:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1316879,1320783}Go on, Captain Langlois!\NYou still have your bullet!
